Draft → Active → Closed

Close Requirements:
- Posted Customer Invoice
- Posted Vendor Bills
- Closed Logistics
- Compliance Check Pass
- Non-negative Margin

Post-Close:
- Commission frozen
- Immutable financial fields
- No invoice reassignment
